  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. The slope through (1, 8) and (5, \u22124) is (\u22124 \u2212 8)/(5 \u2212 1) = \u221212/4 = \u22123. Substituting (1, 8) into <em>y</em> = \u22123<em>x</em> + <em>b</em>: 8 = \u22123 + <em>b</em>, so <em>b</em> = 11. Therefore <em>f</em>(<em>x</em>) = \u22123<em>x</em> + 11.</p><p>Choices A, B, and C are incorrect; verifying with the two points shows none of those equations is satisfied by both.</p>",
